column2: "Oh... it's you. I have no interest in you. Where's that masked bastard?"
"But I guess you don't know anything about him, now do you?"
"Someone's out to kill you and you have no idea why, or even who the hell he is? You're pathetic."

"<%me>, if you hide anything,
he will kill you where you stand."
"That's not gonna happen here, Sina. Where would be the fun in that?"
"But based on what happened the other day, it is impossible to conclude that they are unconnected."
"Hmm, Sina? Are you telling me what to do?"

"You do as you like for now.
Once you're ready, I'll have my fun."
